item.description:
Join me out at Muldoon park to toss some discs around. We will meet at the Hillside Store  to make sure everyone has discs and water if needed. We will then go across to the park and play the 18 holes.  Oh and Nobody has to keep score unless you want to.

It's located along a wooded path. Please wear good shoes and bring bug spray. I don't care how well you throw, just that were out having fun and getting some good exercise and laughs.

We can all go back to the store after for sandwiches or icecream !

Come give it a try !

my # 603-315-0275
item.how_to_find_us: Meet me at Hillside store across from the park.
